{"word":"Magician","slug":"magician","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Magician</b> A person who claims to understand and explain mysteries by magic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=1&verse=20'>Dan 1:20</a><br/> Failed to interpret Pharaoh's dreams<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=8'>Gen 41:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=24'>Gen 41:24</a><br/> Failed to interpret Nebuchadnezzar's dream<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=2&verse=13'>Dan 2:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=4&verse=7'>Dan 4:7</a><br/> Wrought apparent miracles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=7&verse=12'>Exo 7:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=7&verse=22'>Exo 7:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=8&verse=7'>Exo 8:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=8&verse=18'>Exo 8:18</a>"}]}